Vigilon Advisory		http://www.vigilon.com/advisories/vg-phpfaber-24-10-2006.txt

-------------------------------------------------------

Application: phpFaber CMS
Web Site:    http://www.phpfaber.com/i/products/cms/
Versions:    1.3.36 and below
Platform:    linux, windows
Bug:         Cross Site Scripting.
Fix Available: Yes
-------------------------------------------------------

